issue.title: Unable to run application
issue.body:
After running grunt it mentioned I needed to install `sass` and `sinatra`:

```
gem install sass
gem install sinatra
```

The web request mentions I am missing a `map.svg` file.

https://github.com/davepagurek/Electioneering/blob/master/server.rb#L4
